          <h2>Guide de Soumission</h2>
          <p style="text-align:justify"><span
              style="background-color:white"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif"><span
                  style="font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif"><span
